{"tid":1638683,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Pro-Beijing force now kidnap, rape & murder HK protesters","createTime":"2019-10-08T11:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T05:31:16.000Z","uid":12609,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8fd76013fb55576c3991491df9061c55fb285d","tid":1638683,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:35:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EBjNLwh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEBjNLwh.png&h=65f94506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Floating body in black clothing is found AGAIN.<br />\nIt has happened so many times since September.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QS9mzRz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQS9mzRz.png&h=b4f8ebc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Female protester was seen kidnapped onto a car by two man.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VuUh7Cw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVuUh7Cw.jpg&h=a8c69f0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">(Translation)<br />\nPro-beijing people: Lets catch some female protester and teach these cockroaches a lesson.<br />\nYou can do whatever you want to them. We have done this a few times already.<br />\nThe police won't bother us.</span>"},{"pid":"0836cded613a454d5081dcc8246c9cd199e7d57a","tid":1638683,"uid":322230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">合法公民抗爭！！！！！你都唔想郁？？？？？？ 唔使旨意想贏！！！！！<br />\n快啲跟住做啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637669</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"2673822d6ae5103705cbaf479df8c225e4b0df3c","tid":1638683,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:09:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"813e6a9f317241ba0f34e3c334299485a600d785","tid":1638683,"uid":73163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"Terrible"},{"pid":"3ac9ce66e83e67a9eb547cc5f202856f3ef44c0d","tid":1638683,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:26:28.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dae04a07045ef38dfa26a7fb72bbb40c42d42dd","tid":1638683,"uid":70127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"These have not been thoroughly verified.<br />\n<br />\nThe verified fact is, dozens have perished suspiciously since Aug 31, all of which classified as &quot;natural death&quot; by the police.<br />\n<br />\nFemale corpses have been found floating on water, making it near impossible to assess whether rapes took place prior to their death.<br />\n<br />\nAnd male corpses found near ground zero, presumably jumping or dropped from high floors of buildings, resulting in severe bone fracture. Some believe that those drops are used to cover up torture prior to death."},{"pid":"c869d321b28e1789196e13d65ef78f3d3f64036c","tid":1638683,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:06:54.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"a4732bb5a72046c4a1ce9d3ed8056f934284e7a7","tid":1638683,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"Posting unverified news here would only harm the creditability of the community. Your audience may not understand the affairs in HK as much as you do and will not be able to differentiate between rumors and facts."},{"pid":"33e87625d642809f94ee5a35884a15651a849528","tid":1638683,"uid":287577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"The reality is not as DragonBall, the dead people will not be resurrected. Some people move on, but